{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1198,"text":"I would be willing to bet\nI'm the dumbest guy in the room,"},{"time":4025,"text":"because I couldn't get through school;\nI struggled with school."},{"time":7011,"text":"But I knew at a very early age\nthat I loved money, I loved business"},{"time":10245,"text":"and I loved this entrepreneurial thing."},{"time":12156,"text":"I was raised to be an entrepreneur."},{"time":13965,"text":"What I've been really\npassionate about ever since --"},{"time":16442,"text":"and I've never spoken\nabout this ever, until now --"},{"time":19283,"text":"so this is the first time\nanyone's heard it,"},{"time":21364,"text":"except my wife, three days ago."},{"time":22886,"text":"She said, \"What are you talking about?\""},{"time":24808,"text":"I told her that I think\nwe miss an opportunity"},{"time":27771,"text":"to find these kids\nwho have the entrepreneurial traits,"},{"time":31000,"text":"and to groom them or show them"},{"time":33000,"text":"that being an entrepreneur\nis actually a cool thing."},{"time":35702,"text":"It's not something\nthat is a bad thing and is vilified,"},{"time":39059,"text":"which is what happens in a lot of society."}]},{"cues":[{"time":41507,"text":"Kids, when we grow up, have dreams,"},{"time":44666,"text":"and we have passions, and we have visions,"},{"time":46696,"text":"and somehow we get those things crushed."},{"time":48653,"text":"We get told that we need to study harder"},{"time":50692,"text":"or be more focused or get a tutor."},{"time":53353,"text":"My parents got me a tutor in French,\nand I still suck in French."},{"time":58472,"text":"Two years ago,"},{"time":59649,"text":"I was the highest-rated lecturer\nat MIT's Entrepreneurial Master's Program."},{"time":63267,"text":"It was a speaking event\nin front of groups of entrepreneurs"},{"time":66094,"text":"from around the world."},{"time":67275,"text":"When I was in grade two,\nI won a citywide speaking competition,"},{"time":70262,"text":"but nobody had ever said,\n\"Hey, this kid's a good speaker."},{"time":73040,"text":"He can't focus, but he loves walking\naround and getting people energized.\""},{"time":76582,"text":"No one said, \"Get him\na coach in speaking.\""},{"time":78626,"text":"They said, get me a tutor\nin what I suck at."}]},{"cues":[{"time":80757,"text":"So as kids show these traits --\nand we need to start looking for them --"},{"time":84530,"text":"I think we should be raising kids\nto be entrepreneurs instead of lawyers."},{"time":88949,"text":"Unfortunately, the school system\nis grooming this world to say,"},{"time":92491,"text":"\"Let's be a lawyer,\"\nor, \"Let's be a doctor.\""},{"time":94639,"text":"We're missing that opportunity,"},{"time":96141,"text":"because no one ever says,\n\"Hey, be an entrepreneur.\""},{"time":98598,"text":"Entrepreneurs are people --\nwe have a lot of them in this room --"},{"time":101673,"text":"who have ideas and passions\nor see these needs in the world"},{"time":104514,"text":"and decide to stand up and do it."},{"time":106188,"text":"And we put everything on the line\nto make that stuff happen."},{"time":109062,"text":"We have the ability\nto get the groups of people around us"},{"time":111815,"text":"that want to build that dream with us."},{"time":113712,"text":"And I think if we could get kids\nto embrace the idea at a young age,"},{"time":117419,"text":"of being entrepreneurial,"},{"time":118657,"text":"we could change everything\nin the world that's a problem today."},{"time":121668,"text":"Every problem out there,\nsomebody has the idea for."},{"time":124098,"text":"And as a young kid,\nnobody can say it can't happen,"},{"time":126729,"text":"because you're too dumb to realize\nthat you couldn't figure it out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":130521,"text":"I think we have an obligation\nas parents and a society"},{"time":133105,"text":"to start teaching our kids to fish\ninstead of giving them the fish --"},{"time":137295,"text":"the old parable: \"Give a man\na fish, you feed him for a day."},{"time":140184,"text":"Teach a man to fish,\nyou feed him for a lifetime.\""},{"time":142558,"text":"If we can teach our kids\nto be entrepreneurial,"},{"time":144790,"text":"the ones that show the traits to be,"},{"time":146544,"text":"like we teach the ones who have\nscience gifts to go on in science,"},{"time":149695,"text":"what if we saw the ones\nwith entrepreneurial traits"},{"time":152132,"text":"and taught them to be entrepreneurs?"},{"time":153892,"text":"We could have these kids\nspreading businesses"},{"time":156020,"text":"instead of waiting\nfor government handouts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":158073,"text":"What we do is teach our kids\nthe things they shouldn't do:"},{"time":160827,"text":"don't hit; don't bite; don't swear."},{"time":162639,"text":"Right now we teach our kids\nto go after really good jobs;"},{"time":165697,"text":"the school system teaches them\nto go after things like"},{"time":168301,"text":"being a doctor and being a lawyer\nand being an accountant and a dentist"},{"time":171706,"text":"and a teacher and a pilot."},{"time":172984,"text":"And the media says it's really cool\nif we could go out"},{"time":175668,"text":"and be a model or a singer"},{"time":177191,"text":"or a sports hero like Luongo or Crosby."},{"time":180150,"text":"Our MBA programs do not teach kids\nto be entrepreneurs."},{"time":183750,"text":"The reason I avoided an MBA program,\nother than that I didn't get into any,"},{"time":187336,"text":"since I had a 61 percent\naverage out of high school,"},{"time":189823,"text":"then a 61 percent average"},{"time":191042,"text":"at the only school in Canada\nthat accepted me, Carlton,"},{"time":193741,"text":"is that our MBA programs don't teach\nkids to be entrepreneurs."},{"time":196731,"text":"They teach them to work in corporations."}]},{"cues":[{"time":198682,"text":"So who's starting these companies?\nIt's these random few people."},{"time":201809,"text":"Even in popular literature,\nthe only book I've ever found --"},{"time":204836,"text":"and this should be\non all your reading lists --"},{"time":207059,"text":"the only book I've ever found"},{"time":208473,"text":"that makes the entrepreneur\na hero is \"Atlas Shrugged.\""},{"time":211077,"text":"Everything else in the world\nlooks at entrepreneurs"},{"time":213515,"text":"and says we're bad people."},{"time":214810,"text":"I look at even my family."},{"time":216042,"text":"Both my grandfathers and my dad\nwere entrepreneurs."},{"time":218517,"text":"My brother, sister and I,\nall three of us own companies as well."},{"time":221564,"text":"We all decided to start these things\nbecause it's the only place we fit."},{"time":225155,"text":"We didn't fit in normal work;\nwe couldn't work for somebody else,"},{"time":228251,"text":"we're stubborn and we have\nall these other traits."}]},{"cues":[{"time":230615,"text":"But kids could be entrepreneurs as well."},{"time":232552,"text":"I'm a big part of a couple organizations"},{"time":234489,"text":"called the Entrepreneurs' Organization\nand the Young Presidents' Organization."},{"time":238185,"text":"I just came back from speaking\nin Barcelona at the YPO global conference."},{"time":241654,"text":"And everyone I met over there\nwho's an entrepreneur"},{"time":245000,"text":"struggled with school."},{"time":246540,"text":"I have 18 out of the 19 signs\nof attention deficit disorder diagnosed."},{"time":250143,"text":"So this thing right here\nis freaking me out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":252976,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":255404,"text":"It's probably why I'm a bit panicked,"},{"time":257227,"text":"other than all the caffeine\nI've had and the sugar."},{"time":259655,"text":"But this is really creepy\nfor an entrepreneur."},{"time":262000,"text":"Attention deficit disorder,\nbipolar disorder."},{"time":264167,"text":"Do you know that bipolar disorder\nis nicknamed the CEO disease?"},{"time":267191,"text":"Ted Turner's got it. Steve Jobs has it."},{"time":269889,"text":"All three of the founders\nof Netscape had it."},{"time":273305,"text":"I could go on and on."},{"time":274712,"text":"Kids -- you can see these signs in kids."},{"time":277000,"text":"And we're giving them Ritalin and saying,"},{"time":279152,"text":"\"Don't be an entrepreneurial type."},{"time":281269,"text":"Fit into this other system\nand try to become a student.\""},{"time":283943,"text":"Sorry, entrepreneurs aren't students."},{"time":285739,"text":"We fast-track. We figure out the game."},{"time":287596,"text":"I stole essays. I cheated on exams."},{"time":289668,"text":"I hired kids to do my accounting\nassignments in university"},{"time":292469,"text":"for 13 consecutive assignments."},{"time":294000,"text":"But as an entrepreneur, you don't do\naccounting, you hire accountants."},{"time":297379,"text":"So I just figured that out earlier."}]},{"cues":[{"time":299310,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":301000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":302809,"text":"At least I can admit I cheated\nin university; most of you won't."},{"time":306023,"text":"I'm also quoted -- and I told\nthe person who wrote the textbook --"},{"time":309381,"text":"I'm now quoted in that exact same\nuniversity textbook"},{"time":311937,"text":"in every Canadian university\nand college studies --"},{"time":314767,"text":"in managerial accounting,\nI'm chapter eight."},{"time":317000,"text":"I open up chapter eight,\ntalking about budgeting."},{"time":319310,"text":"I told the author,\nafter they did my interview,"},{"time":321529,"text":"that I cheated in that same course."},{"time":323251,"text":"She thought it was too funny\nto not include it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":325666,"text":"But kids, you can see these signs in them."},{"time":328039,"text":"The definition of entrepreneur\nis \"a person who organizes, operates"},{"time":331362,"text":"and assumes the risk\nof a business venture.\""},{"time":333600,"text":"That doesn't mean you have\nto go to an MBA program,"},{"time":336030,"text":"or that you have to get through school."},{"time":337924,"text":"It just means that those few things\nhave to feel right in your gut."},{"time":341119,"text":"We've heard, \"Is it nurture\nor is it nature?\" Right?"},{"time":343609,"text":"Is it thing one or thing two? What is it?"},{"time":345611,"text":"Well, I don't think it's either.\nI think it can be both."},{"time":348264,"text":"I was groomed as an entrepreneur."}]},{"cues":[{"time":349891,"text":"When I was growing up\nas a young kid, I had no choice,"},{"time":352675,"text":"because I was taught at a very early age,"},{"time":354675,"text":"when my dad realized I didn't fit\ninto everything else"},{"time":357309,"text":"that was being taught to me in school,"},{"time":359168,"text":"that he could teach me\nto figure out business at an early age."},{"time":362143,"text":"He groomed us, the three of us,\nto hate the thought of having a job"},{"time":365415,"text":"and to love the fact of creating companies"},{"time":367448,"text":"where we could employ other people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":369147,"text":"My first business venture:\nI was seven years old, in Winnipeg."},{"time":372105,"text":"I was in my bedroom\nwith one of those long extension cords,"},{"time":374902,"text":"calling all the dry cleaners in Winnipeg"},{"time":376853,"text":"to find out how much they'd pay\nme for coat hangers."},{"time":379309,"text":"And my mom came into the room and said,"},{"time":381310,"text":"\"Where are you going to get the hangers\nto sell to the dry cleaners?\""},{"time":384634,"text":"And I said, \"Let's go look\nin the basement.\""},{"time":386757,"text":"We went down to the basement,\nand I opened up this cupboard."},{"time":389607,"text":"There was about 1,000 hangers\nthat I'd collected,"},{"time":391949,"text":"because, when I told her\nI was going out to play,"},{"time":394275,"text":"I was going door to door\nin the neighborhood"},{"time":396355,"text":"to collect hangers to put in the basement,"},{"time":398441,"text":"because I saw her\na few weeks before that --"},{"time":401061,"text":"you could get paid, they used to pay\ntwo cents per coat hanger."},{"time":404063,"text":"So I was like, well,\nthere's all kinds of hangers,"},{"time":406449,"text":"so I'll just go get them."},{"time":407675,"text":"I knew she wouldn't want me to get them,"},{"time":409611,"text":"so I just did it anyway."},{"time":410840,"text":"And I learned that you could\nactually negotiate with people."},{"time":413675,"text":"This one guy offered me three cents\nand I got him up to three and a half."},{"time":417171,"text":"I even knew at seven years old"},{"time":418641,"text":"that I could get\na fractional percent of a cent,"},{"time":420919,"text":"and people would pay it,\nbecause it multiplied up."},{"time":423290,"text":"At seven years old I figured it out."},{"time":425045,"text":"I got three and a half cents\nfor 1,000 hangers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":427278,"text":"I sold license plate\nprotectors door to door."},{"time":429414,"text":"My dad actually made me go find someone"},{"time":431325,"text":"who would sell me them at wholesale."},{"time":433109,"text":"At nine years old, I walked\naround in the city of Sudbury"},{"time":435822,"text":"selling license-plate\nprotectors door to door."},{"time":438004,"text":"And I remember\nthis one customer so vividly --"},{"time":440208,"text":"I also did some other stuff\nwith these clients, I sold newspapers,"},{"time":443783,"text":"and he wouldn't buy\na newspaper from me, ever."},{"time":445959,"text":"But I was convinced I was going to get him\nto buy a license-plate protector."},{"time":449563,"text":"And he's like, \"We don't need one.\""},{"time":451264,"text":"I said, \"But you've got two cars.\""},{"time":452936,"text":"Remember, I'm nine years old."},{"time":454366,"text":"I'm like, \"You have two cars and they\ndon't have license-plate protectors."},{"time":457898,"text":"And this car has one license plate\nthat's all crumpled up.\""},{"time":460736,"text":"He said, \"That's my wife's car.\""},{"time":462314,"text":"I said, \"Why don't we test one on her car\nand see if it lasts longer?\""},{"time":465675,"text":"So I knew there were two cars\nwith two license plates on each."},{"time":468675,"text":"If I couldn't sell all four,\nI could at least get one."},{"time":471293,"text":"I learned that at a young age."}]},{"cues":[{"time":472765,"text":"I did comic book arbitrage."},{"time":474083,"text":"When I was about 10 years old,\nI sold comic books"},{"time":476427,"text":"out of our cottage on Georgian Bay."},{"time":478191,"text":"I would go biking\nup to the end of the beach,"},{"time":480320,"text":"buy all the comics from the poor kids,"},{"time":482218,"text":"then go back to the other end of the beach\nto sell them to the rich kids."},{"time":485675,"text":"It was obvious to me: buy low, sell high."},{"time":487675,"text":"You've got this demand\nover here that has money."},{"time":489947,"text":"Don't try to sell to the poor kids;\nthey don't have cash."},{"time":492717,"text":"The rich people do. Obvious, right?"},{"time":494584,"text":"It's like a recession."},{"time":495771,"text":"So there's a recession."},{"time":496962,"text":"There's still 13 trillion dollars\ncirculating in the US economy."},{"time":500002,"text":"Go get some of that.\nI learned that at a young age."},{"time":502614,"text":"I also learned, don't reveal your source:"},{"time":504628,"text":"I got beat up after four weeks of this,"},{"time":506535,"text":"because one of the rich kids found out\nwhere I was buying my comics,"},{"time":509866,"text":"and didn't like that he was paying more."}]},{"cues":[{"time":511811,"text":"I was forced to get\na paper route at 10 years old."},{"time":514198,"text":"I didn't want a paper route, but my dad\nsaid, \"That's your next business.\""},{"time":517742,"text":"Not only did he get me one,\nbut I had to get two."},{"time":520090,"text":"He wanted me to hire someone\nto deliver half the papers,"},{"time":522805,"text":"which I did."},{"time":523980,"text":"Then I realized: collecting tips\nis how you made all the money."},{"time":527012,"text":"So I'd collect tips and get payment."},{"time":528764,"text":"I would collect for the papers --\nhe could just deliver them."},{"time":531675,"text":"Because then I realized\nI could make money."},{"time":533714,"text":"By this point, I was definitely\nnot going to be an employee."}]},{"cues":[{"time":536572,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":537968,"text":"My dad owned an automotive\nand industrial repair shop."},{"time":540524,"text":"He had all these old\nautomotive parts lying around."},{"time":542964,"text":"They had this old brass and copper."},{"time":544663,"text":"I asked what he did with it,\nand he said he just throws it out."},{"time":547664,"text":"I said, \"Wouldn't somebody pay\nfor that?\" And he goes, \"Maybe.\""},{"time":550674,"text":"Remember: at 10 years old, 34 years ago,"},{"time":552627,"text":"I saw opportunity in this stuff,\nI saw there was money in garbage."},{"time":555750,"text":"And I collected it from the automotive\nshops in the area on my bicycle."},{"time":559126,"text":"Then my dad would drive me on Saturdays\nto a scrap metal recycler"},{"time":562235,"text":"where I got paid."},{"time":563414,"text":"And I thought that was kind of cool."},{"time":565158,"text":"Strangely enough, 30 years later,\nwe're building 1-800-GOT-JUNK?"},{"time":568231,"text":"and making money off that, too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":569743,"text":"I built these little pincushions\nwhen I was 11 years old in Cubs."},{"time":572821,"text":"We made these pincushions\nfor our moms for Mother's Day"},{"time":575441,"text":"out of wooden clothespins --"},{"time":577121,"text":"when we used to hang clothes\non clotheslines outside."},{"time":579639,"text":"And you'd make these chairs."},{"time":581029,"text":"And I had these little pillows\nthat I would sew up."},{"time":583451,"text":"And you could stuff pins in them."},{"time":585073,"text":"Because people used to sew\nand they needed a pincushion."},{"time":589057,"text":"But I realized you had to have options,"},{"time":591178,"text":"so I spray-painted\na whole bunch of them brown,"},{"time":593422,"text":"so when I went to the door,\nit wasn't, \"Do you want to buy one?\""},{"time":596450,"text":"It was, \"Which color would you like?\""},{"time":598250,"text":"I'm 10 years old;\nyou're not going to say no,"},{"time":600382,"text":"especially if you have two options,\nthe brown one or the clear one."},{"time":603587,"text":"So I learned that lesson at a young age."}]},{"cues":[{"time":605536,"text":"I learned that manual labor really sucks."},{"time":607918,"text":"Right, like cutting lawns is brutal."},{"time":610931,"text":"But because I had to cut lawns\nall summer for all of our neighbors"},{"time":614069,"text":"and get paid to do that,"},{"time":615276,"text":"I realized that recurring revenue\nfrom one client is amazing,"},{"time":618770,"text":"that if I land this client once,"},{"time":621190,"text":"and every week I get paid by that person,"},{"time":623337,"text":"that's way better than trying to sell\none clothespin thing to one person,"},{"time":627675,"text":"because you can't sell them more."},{"time":629320,"text":"So I love that recurring revenue model\nI started to learn at a young age."}]},{"cues":[{"time":632813,"text":"Remember, I was being groomed to do this.\nI was not allowed to have jobs."},{"time":636297,"text":"I would go to the golf course\nand caddy for people,"},{"time":638739,"text":"but I realized there was this one hill\non our golf course, the 13th hole,"},{"time":642253,"text":"that had this huge hill,"},{"time":643451,"text":"and people could never\nget their bags up it."},{"time":645548,"text":"So I'd sit there in a lawn chair\nand carry for all the people"},{"time":648461,"text":"who didn't have caddies."},{"time":649661,"text":"I'd carry their golf bags to the top;\nthey'd pay me a dollar,"},{"time":652556,"text":"while my friends worked for hours\nhauling some guy's bag around"},{"time":655541,"text":"for 10 bucks."},{"time":656723,"text":"I'm like, \"That's stupid.\nYou have to work for five hours."},{"time":659468,"text":"That doesn't make sense. Figure out\na way to make more money faster."}]},{"cues":[{"time":662693,"text":"Every week, I'd go to the corner store\nand buy all these pops,"},{"time":665628,"text":"Then I'd deliver them\nto these 70-year-old women playing bridge."},{"time":668675,"text":"They'd give me their orders\nfor the following week."},{"time":671143,"text":"I'd deliver pop and charge twice."},{"time":672801,"text":"I had this captured market."},{"time":674134,"text":"You didn't need contracts, you just needed\nto have a supply and demand"},{"time":677818,"text":"and this audience who bought into you."},{"time":679675,"text":"These women weren't going\nto go to anybody else"},{"time":681895,"text":"because they liked me,\nand I kind of figured it out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":684397,"text":"I went and got golf balls\nfrom golf courses."},{"time":686539,"text":"But everybody else was looking in the bush"},{"time":688675,"text":"and looking in the ditches for golf balls."},{"time":690751,"text":"I'm like, screw that. They're in the pond.\nAnd nobody's going into the pond."},{"time":694482,"text":"So I'd go into the ponds and crawl\naround and pick them up with my toes,"},{"time":697894,"text":"just pick them up with both feet."},{"time":699511,"text":"You can't do it onstage."},{"time":701345,"text":"You get the golf balls,\nthrow them in your bathing suit trunks"},{"time":704298,"text":"and when you're done, you've got\na couple hundred of them."},{"time":707061,"text":"But the problem is, people\ndidn't want all the golf balls."},{"time":709842,"text":"So I just packaged them.\nI'm like 12, right?"},{"time":711962,"text":"I packaged them up three ways."},{"time":713423,"text":"I had the Pinnacles, DDHs\nand the really cool ones."},{"time":715846,"text":"Those sold for two dollars each."},{"time":717401,"text":"Then I had the good ones\nthat didn't look crappy: 50 cents each."},{"time":720471,"text":"And then I'd sell 50 at a time\nof all the crappy ones."},{"time":723073,"text":"And they could use those\nfor practice balls."}]},{"cues":[{"time":725349,"text":"I sold sunglasses when I was in school,"},{"time":728227,"text":"to all the kids in high school."},{"time":729848,"text":"This is what really kind of gets\neverybody hating you,"},{"time":732459,"text":"because you're trying to extract money\nfrom all your friends all the time."},{"time":735981,"text":"But it paid the bills."},{"time":737187,"text":"So I sold lots and lots of sunglasses."},{"time":739080,"text":"Then when the school shut me down --"},{"time":740858,"text":"they called me into the office\nand told me I couldn't do it --"},{"time":743811,"text":"I went to the gas stations and sold\nlots of them to the gas stations"},{"time":747386,"text":"and had the gas stations\nsell them to their customers."},{"time":749957,"text":"That was cool because then,\nI had retail outlets."},{"time":752345,"text":"I think I was 14."}]},{"cues":[{"time":753520,"text":"Then I paid my entire way through\nfirst year of university at Carlton"},{"time":756800,"text":"by selling wineskins door to door."},{"time":758456,"text":"You know you can hold\na 40-ounce bottle of rum"},{"time":760640,"text":"and two bottles of coke in a wineskin?"},{"time":762497,"text":"So what, right? But you know what?"},{"time":764155,"text":"Stuff that down your shorts\nwhen you go to a football game,"},{"time":766945,"text":"you can get booze in for free."},{"time":768407,"text":"Everybody bought them."},{"time":769631,"text":"Supply, demand, big opportunity."},{"time":771951,"text":"I also branded it, so I sold them\nfor five times the normal cost."},{"time":775076,"text":"It had our university logo on it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":776675,"text":"You know, we teach our kids\nand we buy them games,"},{"time":779068,"text":"but why don't we get them games,\nif they're entrepreneurial kids,"},{"time":782189,"text":"that nurture the traits\nyou need to be entrepreneurs?"},{"time":784700,"text":"Why don't you teach them\nnot to waste money?"},{"time":787014,"text":"I remember being told to walk\nout into the middle of a street"},{"time":789950,"text":"in Banff, Alberta."},{"time":791144,"text":"I'd thrown a penny out in the street,"},{"time":792978,"text":"and my dad said, \"Go pick it up."},{"time":794535,"text":"I work too damn hard for my money.\nI'm not going to see you waste a penny.\""},{"time":798171,"text":"I remember that lesson to this day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":799879,"text":"Allowances teach kids the wrong habits."},{"time":801797,"text":"Allowances, by nature,\nare teaching kids to think about a job."},{"time":805392,"text":"An entrepreneur doesn't expect\na regular paycheck."},{"time":808393,"text":"Allowance is breeding kids at a young age\nto expect a regular paycheck."},{"time":812098,"text":"That's wrong, for me,\nif you want to raise entrepreneurs."},{"time":814811,"text":"What I do with my kids, nine and seven,"},{"time":816822,"text":"is teach them to walk\naround the house and the yard,"},{"time":819316,"text":"looking for stuff that needs to get done."},{"time":821317,"text":"Come and tell me what it is."},{"time":822728,"text":"Or I'll say, \"Here's what I need done.\""},{"time":824675,"text":"And then, you know\nwhat we do? We negotiate."},{"time":826797,"text":"They go around looking for what it is,"},{"time":828675,"text":"then we negotiate what they'll get paid."},{"time":830675,"text":"They don't have a regular check,"},{"time":832325,"text":"but they have opportunities\nto find more stuff,"},{"time":834587,"text":"and learn the skill of negotiating\nand of finding opportunities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":837675,"text":"You breed that kind of stuff."},{"time":839105,"text":"Each of my kids has two piggy banks."},{"time":840898,"text":"Fifty percent of all the money they earn\ngoes in their house account,"},{"time":844377,"text":"50 percent goes in their toy account."},{"time":846179,"text":"The toy account,\nthey spend on whatever they want."},{"time":848574,"text":"The 50 percent in their house account,\nevery six months, goes to the bank."},{"time":852106,"text":"they walk up with me."},{"time":853281,"text":"Every year, all the money\nin the bank goes to their broker."},{"time":856103,"text":"Both my nine- and seven-year-olds\nhave a stockbroker already."},{"time":859095,"text":"I'm teaching them\nto force that savings habit."},{"time":861319,"text":"It drives me crazy\nthat 30-year-olds are saying,"},{"time":863630,"text":"\"Maybe I'll start contributing\nto my RSP now.\""},{"time":865846,"text":"Shit, you've missed 25 years."},{"time":867601,"text":"You can teach those habits to young kids,"},{"time":869590,"text":"when they don't even feel the pain yet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":871488,"text":"Don't read bedtime stories every night --\nmaybe four nights of the week,"},{"time":875674,"text":"and three nights, have them tell stories."},{"time":877977,"text":"Why don't you sit down with kids\nand give them four items,"},{"time":880761,"text":"a red shirt, a blue tie,\na kangaroo and a laptop,"},{"time":883675,"text":"and have them tell a story\nabout those four things?"},{"time":886128,"text":"My kids do that all the time."},{"time":887550,"text":"It teaches them to sell,\nteaches them creativity,"},{"time":889891,"text":"teaches them to think on their feet."},{"time":891730,"text":"Do that kind of stuff, have fun with it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":893675,"text":"Get kids to stand up\nin front of groups and talk,"},{"time":896017,"text":"even if it's just\nin front of their friends,"},{"time":898116,"text":"and do plays and have speeches."},{"time":899622,"text":"Those are entrepreneurial traits\nyou want to be nurturing."},{"time":902391,"text":"Show kids what bad customers\nor bad employees look like."},{"time":905063,"text":"Show them grumpy employees."},{"time":906421,"text":"When you see grumpy\ncustomer service, point it out."},{"time":908925,"text":"Say, \"By the way,\nthat guy is a crappy employee.\""},{"time":911271,"text":"And say, \"These are good ones.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":912855,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":914912,"text":"If you go into a restaurant\nand have bad customer service,"},{"time":917670,"text":"show them what bad\ncustomer service looks like."}]},{"cues":[{"time":919934,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":921850,"text":"We have all these lessons in front of us,"},{"time":923850,"text":"but we don't take those opportunities;\nwe teach kids to get a tutor."},{"time":927110,"text":"Imagine if you actually took\nall the kids' junk in the house right now,"},{"time":930508,"text":"all the toys they outgrew two years ago"},{"time":932414,"text":"and said, \"Why don't we sell\nsome of this on Craigslist and Kijiji?\""},{"time":935659,"text":"And they actually sell it and learn\nhow to find scammers when offers come in."},{"time":939374,"text":"They can come into your account\nor a sub account or whatever."},{"time":942282,"text":"But teach them how to fix\nthe price, guess the price,"},{"time":944791,"text":"pull up the photos."},{"time":946675,"text":"Teach them how to do\nthat kind of stuff and make money."},{"time":949355,"text":"Then 50 percent\ngoes in their house account,"},{"time":951444,"text":"50 percent in their toy account."},{"time":953026,"text":"My kids love this stuff."}]},{"cues":[{"time":954258,"text":"Some of the entrepreneurial traits\nyou've got to nurture in kids:"},{"time":957348,"text":"attainment, tenacity, leadership,\nintrospection, interdependence, values."},{"time":960818,"text":"All these traits, you can find in young\nkids, and you can help nurture them."},{"time":964439,"text":"Look for that kind of stuff."},{"time":965803,"text":"There's two traits I want you\nto also look out for"},{"time":968217,"text":"that we don't get out of their system."},{"time":970432,"text":"Don't medicate kids\nfor attention deficit disorder"},{"time":972838,"text":"unless it is really, really freaking bad."}]},{"cues":[{"time":974839,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":976435,"text":"The same with the whole things\non mania and stress and depression,"},{"time":979577,"text":"unless it is so clinically brutal, man."},{"time":981578,"text":"Bipolar disorder is nicknamed\n\"the CEO disease.\""},{"time":984061,"text":"When Steve Jurvetson, Jim Clark\nand Jim Barksdale have all got it,"},{"time":988635,"text":"and they built Netscape --"},{"time":990075,"text":"imagine if they were given Ritalin."},{"time":991809,"text":"We wouldn't have that stuff, right?"},{"time":993675,"text":"Al Gore really would have had\nto invented the Internet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":996452,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":998214,"text":"These are the skills\nwe should be teaching in the classroom,"},{"time":1001153,"text":"as well as everything else."},{"time":1002472,"text":"I'm not saying don't get kids\nto want to be lawyers."},{"time":1004992,"text":"But how about getting entrepreneurship\nto be ranked right up there"},{"time":1008169,"text":"with the rest of them?"},{"time":1009345,"text":"Because there's huge\nopportunities in that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1011399,"text":"I want to close with a quick video"},{"time":1013130,"text":"that was done by one\nof the companies I mentor."},{"time":1015385,"text":"These guys, Grasshopper."},{"time":1016903,"text":"It's about kids."},{"time":1018092,"text":"It's about entrepreneurship."},{"time":1019482,"text":"Hopefully, this inspires you\nto take what you've heard from me"},{"time":1022431,"text":"and do something with it\nto change the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1024904,"text":"[Kid... \"And you thought\nyou could do anything?\"]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1027222,"text":"[You still can.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1029223,"text":"[Because a lot of what\nwe consider impossible]"},{"time":1032080,"text":"[is easy to overcome]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1034675,"text":"[Because in case you haven't\nnoticed, we live in a place where]"},{"time":1037699,"text":"[one individual can make a difference]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1040461,"text":"[Want proof?]"},{"time":1041684,"text":"[Just look at the people\nwho built our country:]"},{"time":1043995,"text":"[Our parents, grandparents,\nour aunts, uncles]"},{"time":1046212,"text":"[They were immigrants, newcomers\nready to make their mark]"},{"time":1049006,"text":"[Maybe they came with very little]"},{"time":1051675,"text":"[or perhaps they didn't own\nanything except for]"},{"time":1053959,"text":"[a single brilliant idea]"},{"time":1056849,"text":"[These people were thinkers, doers]"},{"time":1060508,"text":"[innovators]"},{"time":1062389,"text":"[until they came up with the name]"},{"time":1066149,"text":"[entrepreneurs]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1069164,"text":"[They change the way we think\nabout what is possible.]"},{"time":1071742,"text":"[They have a clear vision\nof how life can be better]"},{"time":1074313,"text":"[for all of us, even when\ntimes are tough.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1076532,"text":"[Right now, it's hard to see]"},{"time":1077988,"text":"[when our view is cluttered\nwith obstacles.]"},{"time":1080743,"text":"[But turbulence creates opportunities]"},{"time":1085013,"text":"[for success, achievement, and pushes us]"},{"time":1088659,"text":"[to discover new ways of doing things]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1090966,"text":"[So what opportunities\nwill you go after and why?]"},{"time":1093727,"text":"[If you're an entrepreneur]"},{"time":1096174,"text":"[you know that risk isn't the reward.]"},{"time":1099080,"text":"[No. The rewards are driving innovation]"},{"time":1101948,"text":"[changing people's lives. Creating jobs.]"},{"time":1104349,"text":"[Fueling growth.]"},{"time":1106531,"text":"[And making a better world.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1109675,"text":"[Entrepreneurs are everywhere.]"},{"time":1111204,"text":"[They run small businesses\nthat support our economy,]"},{"time":1113761,"text":"[design tools to help you]"},{"time":1115027,"text":"[stay connected with friends,\nfamily and colleagues]"},{"time":1117489,"text":"[And they're finding new ways of helping\nto solve society's oldest problems.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1121149,"text":"[Do you know an entrepreneur?]"},{"time":1122608,"text":"[Entrepreneurs can be anyone\nEven... you]"},{"time":1124683,"text":"[So seize the opportunity to create\nthe job you always wanted]"},{"time":1127756,"text":"[Help heal the economy]"},{"time":1129344,"text":"[Make a difference.]"},{"time":1130520,"text":"[Take your business to new heights,]"},{"time":1133603,"text":"[but most importantly,]"},{"time":1134896,"text":"[remember when you were a kid]"},{"time":1138516,"text":"[when everything was within your reach,]"},{"time":1141548,"text":"[and then say to yourself\nquietly, but with determination:]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1147595,"text":"[it still is.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1152150,"text":"Thank you very much for having me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1153826,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}